{"tid":2439566,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"妻致函尹兆堅：以你為榮","createTime":"2021-03-09T10:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T10:44:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6bda891ffa5cc59f8a5742a3e33b5db4fec89620","tid":2439566,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/VUFQ35FVEZFF3IKBNDNJCJXJIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FVUFQ35FVEZFF3IKBNDNJCJXJIE%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy2Ckd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=a5304823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FVUFQ35FVEZFF3IKBNDNJCJXJIE%2F&h=077bf91a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/VUFQ35FVEZFF3IKBNDNJCJXJIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n妻致函尹兆堅：以你為榮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PZlTfNOb76xx1dMtMPViFvpd5EU=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SXSZEM5VKVAE7BPKSOOZTLTVJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPZlTfNOb76xx1dMtMPViFvpd5EU%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSXSZEM5VKVAE7BPKSOOZTLTVJU.jpg&h=61a6c2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■尹兆堅目前還柙，其妻擔心他能否適應獨立囚禁。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被捕民主派家屬透過紙筆傳情，民主黨尹兆堅妻子在首封寫給丈夫的家書中，訴說自己和一對子女對尹的思念。尹太尤其不習慣家中沒了丈夫的身影、聲音和氣味，「如今，沒有你的日子，我會在家中穿上你的衣裳，希望感覺你與我同在」。尹太強調，對於能夠成為尹兆堅妻子感到驕傲，一對子女亦以爸爸一生行公義為榮，「You are our HERO，我們期待能盡快一家團聚。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：歐美逾千人聲援民主派<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「千萬不要愧疚」<br />\n<br />\n尹太在尹的Patreon發佈家書，憶丈夫家中生活點滴，「你慣常坐梳化的位置；工作後回家，穿着西裝、拎着一袋二袋食物進門的情境；在廚房為我們準備飯餐的背影；出門前，悉心梳整的情況：分段式吹頭、Gel行頭髮和噴香水，都歷歷在目。」<br />\n<br />\n她說圍牆外的家人「不能切切實實體會你每分每秒怎樣熬過」，又擔心丈夫。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：11子保釋覆核 高院改分三日審<br />\n<br />\n尹太稱會堅強面對，好好過活，讓丈夫能無後顧之憂，又說身為尹的太太感到驕傲，他的一對子女「知道你一生行公義，全以你為榮」，又知丈夫一定會對他們愧疚，「但千萬、千萬不要這樣想，你絕不是我們的負累而是光榮。」強調會不斷入書和寫信，相信尹重獲自由之時，「必定會是一個更強大、更懂珍惜、更健康靚仔的你。」據知尹太以後持續在Patreon分享尹兆堅狀況，感激各方支持尹。"},{"pid":"4d657103ca4f7cd1ab38beb45d9704cc79933d4a","tid":2439566,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"You are our hero<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b200a33bede82ba97f5ce458b926e898baca3b","tid":2439566,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"proud of you<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}